description: Catherine Martin is vying to replace Eamon Ryan as the Greens' leader in the Republic of Ireland.
title: Catherine Martin: The woman hoping to lead Ireland's Green Party
title_page: Catherine Martin: The woman hoping to lead Ireland's Green Party - BBC News
